1 This act would require that pharmacy benefit managers ensure that the total amount
2 required to be paid by a health benefit plan and a covered person for a prescription drug covered
3 under the plan does not exceed the amount paid to the pharmacy for dispensing the drug.
4 This act would take effect upon passage.
